data.description: If you are looking for a quiet country setting AND convenience, look no further!  This beautifully renovated home sits on just under 5 acres with its own private creek, yet it's a mere 5 minutes to Walmart, I-75 and restaurants. Only 15 minutes to Norris Lake and 25 minutes from Oak Ridge. New roof, HVAC and plumbing. Enough land to build a 2nd home for multifamily living, an investment property rental, and so much more. Approx 138 feet from driveway to the right edge of the property line. Flat and cleared! Secure your place in the small but growing town of Clinton, TN.
